		<div id="comment_body_64771574"><p><div class="quote"><p>when contacting Tomtom support to get the latest map released for the device they just offer you a 35% discount off a new device.</p></div><p>I suspect you already have the latest map released <b>"for the device"</b>. That's the issue with "lifetime". It's not talking about your lifetime. It's talking about the product lifetime which ends when the product is discontinued.</p><p>Sucks, but that's how most companies operate in their "lifetime" promises.</p></div>
	</div>

